#. <section class="sutta" id="sn22.67"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.67:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.67:0.2"
msgid "7. Arahantavagga"
msgstr "7. The Perfected Ones"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.67:0.3"
msgid "67. Dukkhasutta"
msgstr "67. Suffering"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.67:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn22.67:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu "
"bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha … and said to him:"

msgctxt "sn22.67:1.3"
msgid ""
"“sādhu me, bhante, bhagavā saṅkhittena dhammaṃ desetu … pe … ātāpī pahitatto "
"vihareyyan”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, may the Buddha please teach me Dhamma in brief. When I’ve heard it, I’"
"ll live alone, withdrawn, diligent, keen, and resolute.”"

msgctxt "sn22.67:1.4"
msgid "“Yaṃ kho, bhikkhu, dukkhaṃ; tatra te chando pahātabbo”ti."
msgstr "“Mendicant, give up desire for anything that’s suffering.”"

msgctxt "sn22.67:1.5"
msgid "“Aññātaṃ, bhagavā, aññātaṃ, sugatā”ti."
msgstr "“Understood, Blessed One! Understood, Holy One!”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.67:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Yathā kathaṃ pana tvaṃ, bhikkhu, mayā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa vitthārena "
"atthaṃ ājānāsī”ti?"
msgstr "“But how do you see the detailed meaning of my brief statement?”"

msgctxt "sn22.67:2.2"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ kho, bhante, dukkhaṃ; tatra me chando pahātabbo."
msgstr "“Sir, form is suffering; I should give up desire for it."

msgctxt "sn22.67:2.3"
msgid "Vedanā …"
msgstr "Feeling …"

msgctxt "sn22.67:2.4"
msgid "saññā …"
msgstr "Perception …"

msgctxt "sn22.67:2.5"
msgid "saṅkhārā …"
msgstr "Choices …"

msgctxt "sn22.67:2.6"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ dukkhaṃ; tatra me chando pahātabbo."
msgstr "Consciousness is suffering; I should give up desire for it."

msgctxt "sn22.67:2.7"
msgid ""
"Imassa khvāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa evaṃ vitthārena "
"atthaṃ ājānāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how I understand the detailed meaning of the Buddha’s brief "
"statement.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.67:3.1"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, bhikkhu."
msgstr "“Good, good, monk!"

msgctxt "sn22.67:3.2"
msgid ""
"Sādhu kho tvaṃ, bhikkhu, mayā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa vitthārena atthaṃ "
"ājānāsi."
msgstr ""
"It’s good that you understand the detailed meaning of what I’ve said in "
"brief like this."

msgctxt "sn22.67:3.3"
msgid "Rūpaṃ kho, bhikkhu, dukkhaṃ; tatra te chando pahātabbo."
msgstr "Form is suffering; you should give up desire for it."

msgctxt "sn22.67:3.4"
msgid "Vedanā …"
msgstr "Feeling …"

msgctxt "sn22.67:3.5"
msgid "saññā …"
msgstr "Perception …"

msgctxt "sn22.67:3.6"
msgid "saṅkhārā …"
msgstr "Choices …"

msgctxt "sn22.67:3.7"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ dukkhaṃ; tatra te chando pahātabbo."
msgstr "Consciousness is suffering; you should give up desire for it."

msgctxt "sn22.67:3.8"
msgid ""
"Imassa kho, bhikkhu, mayā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa evaṃ vitthārena attho "
"daṭṭhabbo”ti … pe …"
msgstr ""
"This is how to understand the detailed meaning of what I said in brief.” …"

msgctxt "sn22.67:3.9"
msgid "aññataro ca pana so bhikkhu arahataṃ ahosīti."
msgstr "And that mendicant became one of the perfected."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.67:3.10"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
